text: Prince Norodom Yuvaneath (, October 17, 1943 â€“ January 13, 2021) was a Cambodian royal. He was the first son of the late king of Cambodia, Norodom Sihanouk and Princess Sisowath Pongsanmoni. He is the half-brother of the current king, Norodom Sihamoni. Yuvaneath was born in Phnom Penh. Yuvaneath died on January 13, 2021 in California, aged 77.Prince Norodom Yuvaneath succumbs to illness ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Cambodian royalty
